      <h2>About This Story</h2>
      <p>Moana (2016) is one of Disney's most beloved animated films. The story of a brave Polynesian girl who saves the world resonates with audiences of all ages. Its themes of identity, environmental stewardship, and the power of compassion make it a timeless tale that will be brought to life again in the 2026 live action remake.</p>
